Package: centerline
Title: Extract Centerline From A Closed Polygons
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Anatoly", "Tsyplenkov", , "atsyplenkov@gmail.com", role = c("cre", "aut"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4144-8402"))
Maintainer: Anatoly Tsyplenkov <atsyplenkov@gmail.com>
Description: The {centerline} R package simplifies the extraction of linear features from closed 2D polygons, such as lakes, by computing their centerlines (or median-axis) using Voronoi diagrams. 
